@node DISTRIBUTION

  DISTRIBUTION:

  WBView demo is FREEWARE but full version can be SHAREWARE (but cheap -
  fee  maximum  DM15).  You may use and copy this program freely but all
  files must be copied in an unmodified state preferably in LhA archive.
  Use it on your own risk.  If you use this program and you like it send
  me a postcard or message via e-mail.

@endnode

