@node BUGS

  KNOWN BUGS:

  - multipic.library doesn't support "Adobe" JPEGs
  - interleaved GIFs aren't supported now (I'm too lazy :) )
  - window is opened with LAYERS_NOBACKFILL tag set for better speed
    especially with MCP QuickLayers function (sometimes window resizing
    looks strange)
 
@endnode

